Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 沉睡心底的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:30.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 向充滿希望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}無論倒下多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要再次站立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:42.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等待 奇跡豈會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越吧 昨日懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:52.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握住 浮於銀河的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}不要屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馳騁的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,40)}向著夢想之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:01.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:07.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘著這天馬的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:12.86,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 熾熱燃燒的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信決不屈服的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:26.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 決不停滯決不放棄的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:33.76,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}直指Ω 奮勇戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.33,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣&galaxy字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當世間面臨邪惡之神的侵略時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便必定會出現奮起迎戰的戰士 聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 年輕聖鬥士們嶄新的傳說即將展開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行人終於抵達最後一宮雙魚宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙魚座的阿墨爾正在等候他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿墨爾將曾為瑪爾斯麾下軍神的瑪爾斯四天王召喚而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重創蒼摩等人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙再次燃燒起已抑制住的暗屬性小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距地球被黑暗所籠罩只剩1小時30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗屬性小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只 只用一擊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了同伴！光牙隱藏的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗屬性小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡而又龐大的暗屬性小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連光牙自己都無法掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 天馬座 再讓我多欣賞一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的意識 並沒有被黑暗所吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與之前不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擁有著光明的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會輸給黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為自己的第七感已覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以掌控黑暗的力量了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 黑暗的力量龐大且偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你這點實力根本抑制不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你體內深處四溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勃然躍動的暗屬性小宇宙的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 回到你所選擇的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這場戲中扮演的角色 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是暗之戰士！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是阿墨爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切盡在計劃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須…阻止光牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙被黑暗侵蝕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以走向黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你約定好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果暗屬性小宇宙出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我在 卻仍要選擇天馬座嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這倔強的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒吧 憎恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底被黑暗浸染吧 直到再也無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 你一直引導著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們指明了前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙的光芒一次又一次地拯救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 你是光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是光之聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以屈服於黑暗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小宇宙是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗屬性小宇宙被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將天馬座的黑暗力量封印住可不好辦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺少了黑暗力量的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要突破四天王的銅牆鐵壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是無稽之談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們將被四天王抹殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而天馬座會因此憤怒 再次墮入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何掙扎 結局都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座會化作黑暗 故事就此落下帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少擅作主張！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會打爆這些傢伙 連同你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我們的劇本！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 你先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能夠打倒瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 以你光芒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正憑你現在的體力 也沒辦法戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們稍後就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為逃得掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 你呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個可人兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明鏡止水！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅熾焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁之術！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炙流石（Flamed Lapis）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我會將你們戰死的慘狀告知天馬座的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們與光牙已有約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 我們稍後就會追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你是瑪爾斯四天王還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才不會在這種地方倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為他們的故事落下帷幕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電之刃（Lightning Edge）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.18,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應為法語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈焰橫欄（Balus de Flamme）    
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炙流石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廬山百龍霸！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼拳 斗牙疾走！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 我的小宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅爆焰（Lionet Explosion）！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…只剩那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後將小宇宙燃燒殆盡 扳倒了四天王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是精彩的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…真是勇氣可嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我可不太喜歡被人追著死纏爛打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較喜歡主動出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是雙魚座的黃金聖鬥士嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我急著趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借個道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能把你打倒再過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是新世界的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太過焦躁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不恢復冷靜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是會讓人有可乘之機的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使遮掩也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的悲傷和憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都看得到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 以及索尼婭的死驅使著你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你失去冷靜的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…還得算上邁錫尼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁錫尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個無聊的對手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那路貨色竟然是百獸之王獅子座的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…把邁錫尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都給過你忠告了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份憤怒會使你的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥志倒是絲毫未減啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信 你就是那個柔弱的少爺 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我曾經見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你還很小 不記得也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親 美狄亞大人是我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定 要披掛這身雙魚座黃金聖衣來保護姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現姐姐所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 卻未能拯救索尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會像你一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的夢想 希望 意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將由我守護 由我實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰 都不准阻礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不明事理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明為了姐姐也就等同於為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一切都是為了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你能夠得到新世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西並不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就給我老老實實地呆著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到天馬座回來為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不讓你妨礙光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會讓你恣意妄為的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是糾纏不休呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會 絕不會讓你妨礙光牙 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算無法打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光牙打敗瑪爾斯之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓你踏出這裡一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜你 還真是信賴天馬座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為天馬座能戰勝瑪爾斯大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 因為光牙 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙他是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個傻瓜 所以他絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會貫徹自己堅信的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使生於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙身上寄托了我們的 我們大家的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有所信仰 只要有所守護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙就絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙絕不會背叛我們的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將大家的心意轉化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一定會戰勝瑪爾斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我所相信的光牙的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論天馬座的小宇宙如何強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只剩下一小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小時之後 地球毀滅的序曲就要奏響嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 他能打敗瑪爾斯大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑毅力就能拯救世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展翅吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一刻賭上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鷹閃光衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就遂你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們共度一段愉悅的時光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達十二宮的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙終於與瑪爾斯正面對峙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給父子間的爭執畫上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸也奔赴決戰之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜與瑪爾斯的命運之戰的真相終被揭曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 幼小的光牙與阿莉雅的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂暴的軍神！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯和路德維希！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:23:09.13,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激戰！！光牙對軍神瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:23:09.13,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座之拳爆裂而出！！
